snippet.textDisplay: Saw him after 5years today with his daughter. All these years I've been pretending to move on from him but my heart knows I can never love someone as much i loved him. My heart skipped a beat when i saw him today, he was happy with his kid and seeing him happy automatically made my day. This was his fav song, now whenever I listen to this i get flashbacks of the times we spent together, suddenly my heart feels heavy and tears start rolling down my eyes. I hope he stays happy and healthy.
